# Navigate Peptides — Payment Processing

> ⚠️ #1 operational risk. Standard processors WILL ban peptide merchants. The site must be fully compliant before the merchant account activates — Mastercard MMP requires pre-transaction scanning.

## Processor Architecture

```
Customer Checkout
  ├── Credit/Debit Card → AllayPay (NMI gateway) [PRIMARY]
  ├── Cryptocurrency    → Coinbase Commerce (BTC, ETH, USDC)
  └── eCheck/ACH        → Paycron
```

## Primary: AllayPay (NMI Gateway)

- Supports peptide startups specifically, MCC 8099
- **Gateway: Argyle's Gateway (NMI)** — startups must use this
- **10% rolling reserve** — held 6 months, releases begin month 7
- VAR sheet (negotiable rate card) available after 12 months clean processing
- Minimum pricing requirements apply
- **Requires WooCommerce** — their NMI plugin must install on WooCommerce backend
- Approval timeline: 5-10 business days
- Processing rates: expect 6-10% effective rate

### Documentation Required for Underwriting
- Complete Merchant Processing Agreement
- Reserve Form (10%)
- Government ID for each owner
- SS4 Form (EIN verification)
- Voided check or bank letter
- Articles of Incorporation or Operating Agreement
- 3 months business or personal bank statements
- 3 months processing statements (if applicable)
- Fulfillment Agreement (if applicable)
- 2 years financials or tax returns (if applicable)

### Website Requirements (Processor-Mandated)
- Products MUST have scientific, technical descriptions
- Per-product disclaimer: "All products currently listed on this site are for research purposes ONLY."
- Sitewide disclaimer: "All products sold on this website are intended for research and identification purposes only. These products are not intended for human dosing, injection, or ingestion."
- No health/wellness/performance/weight-loss/anti-aging/recovery claims
- No dosage guidance, protocols, cycles, stacks
- No testimonials describing outcomes or effects
- No influencer, social media, or lifestyle marketing
- No blogs, FAQs, or SEO terms implying personal or human use
- Peptides strictly for laboratory, academic, or institutional research

## Crypto: Coinbase Commerce

- Zero chargebacks, no underwriting
- BTC, ETH, USDC supported
- WooCommerce plugin available + Node.js SDK for Next.js
- Activate Day 1 as alternative payment method
- Offer 10% crypto discount (industry standard)
- No processor risk — operates independently of card networks

## ACH: Paycron

- eCheck/ACH only — NOT credit cards for peptide merchants
- 99% approval rate
- Good for high-AOV orders ($150+)
- Secondary payment rail, not primary

